name: TheNailWorld.com
tag_list: beauty, female, hong-kong, china, nail-art, nail, girl, website
overview:
TheNailWorld.com is the ultimate place for nail lovers ! Everything you want to know about your nails, nail trend, nail and hand products, which nail salon to go and their ratings, or make your own nail art DIY at home etc etc.

TheNailWorld.com existed in multiple platforms (Websites, Mobile Apps, Social Media Pages, MiniSites) for nail lovers to share, to communicate and to have fun with their nails, because we believe all girls deserved to have nice and beautiful nails !

Regional Existence: TheNailWorld.com.hk (http://www.thenailworld.com.hk/)is currently the Number 1 Female Nail (Beauty) platform in Hong Kong, China.

Others: With solid plans to diversify into other China region.
